{"tid":2188520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛審查委員會成員包括鍾南山　華春瑩：相信有助貢獻","createTime":"2020-09-04T09:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T06:00:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7f47f4580b4eb218509265927ed30264820b2415","tid":2188520,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"負責審查世衛應對新型肺炎疫情手法的獨立委員會正式組成，預料明年5月提交最終報告。委員會由兩名聯合主席及11名委員組成，委員包括國家衛健委高級別專家組組長鍾南山。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩表示，相信鍾南山的專業精神和經驗，將為世衛專家組的工作提供幫助，並作出積極貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩指出，當前疫情仍在全球蔓延，抗疫仍是各國頭等大事，需要全球、各地區、各國家層面作出協調一致努力，並發揮好世衛在應對疫情上的中心協調作用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547873-20200904.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547873-20200904.htm&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1caCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=adadc541\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547873-20200904.htm&h=2c3a6dcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547873-20200904.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d855056e972884884ab750441c9c23667443526d","tid":2188520,"uid":359022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:46:40.000Z","msg":"對中國貢獻：美國大爆發"},{"pid":"8252c4c99e50e0c50d16991074bf6fbcdc3facca","tid":2188520,"uid":68620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"鐘南山算吧啦<br />\n都唔明條友講幾句個個當佢神咁拜"},{"pid":"6a87959f20dc72f35576e8cf63883353258ca4ea","tid":2188520,"uid":134381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8252c4c99e50e0c50d16991074bf6fbcdc3facca","tid":2188520,"uid":68620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"鐘南山算吧啦<br />\n都唔明條友講幾句個個當佢神咁拜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"又多個PANEL賣佢果套武肺中藥"},{"pid":"29cb98ce5b01e7ab1cb6e9c9f6fb75ec89d35c0a","tid":2188520,"uid":182927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited